Do you mean something like:
--- linux-2.6.0-test3/drivers/pcmcia/Kconfig	2003-08-09 00:39:25.000000000 -0400
+++ temp/drivers/pcmcia/Kconfig	2003-08-12 04:44:03.000000000 -0400
@@ -86,7 +86,7 @@
 
